archimate:DataObject.name: ConsumptionSummary
archimate:DataObject.documentation: A ConsumptionSummary give measures about the usage quantity consumed. It might concern UsageVolumeBalances and / or UsageVolumeProducts and / or NetworkProducts and / or ProductUsers. A ConsumptionSummary aggregates UsageVolumeBalanceCredits and / or UsageVolumeBalanceDebits and / or AppliedCustomerBillingProductUsageRates.
